Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:29.10,staff2,NTP,0,0,0,,那些年冒过的险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标世界级电影导演 释放青春
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小金井纯平 第二次的冒险 准备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:48.83,staff2,NTP,0,0,0,,热烈青春开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君 来游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:00.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:42.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:02:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就两个人在船舱里玩一会儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调整心情 再来激情一次?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 鲨鱼这家伙 紧要关头来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呱 呱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 一大早的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在气头上 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是下一部作品的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 剧本呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.95,0:03:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小金井 下一作制作终止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?终止?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.69,0:04:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追着兔子上了山
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有钱啦! 没有钱!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会 之前的作品不是赚了一大笔吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都拿去还了债啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今后打算怎么办!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是正在想吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~熬夜写的白费了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平 快找地方跳槽好像比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 连前辈也那样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 嗨 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 社长 用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然少 先垫个底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 太走运了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然想这么说 但是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和 好意我心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心 阿波罗企划不会因为这点儿困境就覆灭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有制作资金吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.21,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员集合!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸君 想必大家也知道阿波罗企划现在正面临巨大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.97,0:05:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了渡过困境 需要大家的协助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,协助是要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说大家一起打工筹集资金!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 停下 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车子 拜托了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.24,0:06:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临 请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼呼 好性感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别嫌少哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.03,0:06:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 会兴奋的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噔 噔 噔 噔~像这样~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:11.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真有意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫做小金井纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 是演员的美那佳子小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走运 你的电影我全部都有看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.60,0:07:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大学生的支持者 真高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为电影导演 现在在修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为导演?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我中意你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在牛郎俱乐部打工赚资金什么的\N真是太堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是很满足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为见到美那佳子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bingo!猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带签名的手绢和名片\N而且给我介绍电影界的名人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 单纯的社交辞令而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是工作 出些糊涂主意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦 不喝酒怎么能行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.18,0:08:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就算我倒了 阿波罗也不会倒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了公司 让大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好吃的 美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君 打工如何了 慰问品的宵夜怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:11.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在纯平君的剧本之前 在思考下一作的构成哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为导演的话 要写剧本哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会介绍电影人给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪?不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 把这个修改一下 拿到美那佳子那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剧本：把我带去海那里\N脚本：小金井纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 提起干劲儿加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界电影圈展翅高飞 小金井纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和科波拉谈笑风生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和斯皮尔伯格握手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和卢卡斯交杯换盏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.81,0:09:57.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三百万 不 二百万也可以 无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.48,0:10:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 是吗 不行吗 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前几天打过电话的小金井纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.98,0:10:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不凑巧 老师现在在伊豆的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗 那么回来之后请把这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.22,0:10:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀吼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.71,0:11:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我 弄疼我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁股生的挺可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小兔崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账 给我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 振作一点 超人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不好 难道是在别人家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 H
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了 等等 这里确实是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喝醉了 把你带回来费了大劲儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我…难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.09,0:13:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 和我之间的事情也?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我之间的事情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说和你犯下了人生甜蜜的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕…呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是怀上宝宝了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我喝醉了 记得不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:15:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你和美那佳子很亲近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…连电话号码都
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打工的地方发生了点儿事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.56,0:15:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美那佳子是大导演涉谷正造的前妻知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 涉谷正造的?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.19,0:15:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人之间记得有一个孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 然后离婚后就一个人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在是南都联合的会长情人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是这么回事儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南都大吾和美那佳子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 去吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 将来要做电影导演
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 但是不轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝着目标笔直前进吗 不是很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.67,0:15:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你叫什么名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三上翔子 多多关照 小金井君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 为什么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看了名片了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 有约的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:15:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 翔子小姐吗 像妖精一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.04,0:16:08.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.05,0:16:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和偶像歌手三上翔子\N是什么时候成为朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女孩 是偶像歌手!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 虽然现在还有点儿生涩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 救了三上翔子?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 就到了我的公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 那女孩住了一晚?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但 但是什么都没发生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有没有我又不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和美和小姐以外的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 相信你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.34,0:16:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?我去演电影?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联袂演出是我和高村澈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细说明去问经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平 美那佳子来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要给你介绍制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 纯平 一个人玩闹也适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向美那佳子自我推销吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 没有那种打算
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我们作为踏板吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种说法太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平 离开阿波罗企划也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连社长也那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的事 是对阿波罗企划的背信弃义哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.98,0:17:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 美那小姐的邀请会拒绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白白放过这么好的机会?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是再也不会有的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家虽然那样说 还是会笑着送你离开的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢 我是绝对不会辞掉阿波罗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意我们的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个业界里 大家都在渴望有靠山帮助自己上位的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:06.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没有那种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在介意什么呢 毕竟是纯平君的梦想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 喜欢美和小姐 所以想一直和你一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是认真的\N但是美和小姐却总是不肯直面对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:37.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.25,0:18:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么让我听听你真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.91,0:18:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 去见见美那佳子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要拒绝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 氏木酱说你就拜托给我了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这次我要做电影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让阿波罗的全员作为制作组参加的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为回礼 打算对阿波罗进行资金援助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和氏木酱是工作上的老相识了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人现在虽然在做电视\N助手导演时代可是很有才华的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢您的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谢谢还太早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.23,0:19:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.13,0:19:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板还没有对作品给出条件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南都大吾会长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 原来知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗企划的命运\N全都被掌握在南都大吾的答复上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还以为自己能招揽年轻的观众吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且就算是顶尖高手之中\N也得是涉谷导演才行呐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还真是怀旧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如我所说 你们的时代已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.99,0:20:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观众的年龄层也在不断变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.75,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.65,0:20:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了给感染年轻观众\N把偶像歌手三上翔子提用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作团队召集对电影制作有热情的年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经没有吸引年轻男人的魅力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能那么简单断言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么如何证明美那佳子\N能让年轻男人勃起 有那种手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.82,0:20:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 证明给我看看\N让我认同的话 就出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.43,0:20:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 在你面前让这个年轻男人勃起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.29,0:20:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 做来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看别处!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事 他不是完全没有亢奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始哟 不要着急
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.84,0:21:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.05,0:21:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.25,0:22:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.80,0:22:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对美那小姐的裸体很感动 但是下面没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了 你用崇高的心灵感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我的存在超越了性欲发泄的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.23,0:22:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随心所欲也给我适可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是你没有魅力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.39,0:22:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 南都先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美那小姐很性感 也很有气质 魅力充分
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.93,0:22:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那为什么不能让你勃起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 有什么不足
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么…我觉得不够
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.72,0:22:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 美那佳子的全裸 从对面的大楼上看的清清楚楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.05,0:22:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我受辱蒙羞吗 不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 好好看看这副身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.22,0:22:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请闭上嘴看着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:22:57.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 还不停下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:23:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 你做什么 停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.28,0:23:02.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在窗边的做爱也是一等哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用勃起的凶器撑着佳子的身体!\N好厉害的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下 会断掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.20,0:23:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美那小姐的神出入化的演技 魅力十足哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的千斤顶 真是太出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我输了 电影的制作费用出十五亿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.03,0:23:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美那小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年的阳痿 看了刚才的佳子\N重整雄风了 看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 生机勃勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~这真是极好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的~ 佳子~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.73,0:24:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽 亲爱的~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戏言成真吗 变得有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.28,0:24:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:19.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜~ 傻瓜~傻瓜~
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.97,0:24:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.08,0:24:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史诗巨作——“谁让你看到了眼泪”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.74,0:24:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主演 三上翔子\N联袂出演 美那佳子 高村澈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.33,0:24:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后导演决定是巨匠涉谷正造
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.54,0:24:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在阿波罗企划全面协助的结果下\N终于在夏天开拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.10,0:24:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后美和小姐被涉谷导演选为分镜编辑\N我作为剧务被提拔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.75,0:24:49.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么庆祝开拍 干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.43,0:24:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.53,0:24:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉谷正造用雏鸟偶像拍电影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.33,0:24:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且助演是老太婆真是伤心呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.58,0:25:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙 太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.66,0:25:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 当耳边风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.90,0:25:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们完全被晾在一边了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.03,0:25:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.07,0:25:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 小金井君
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.72,0:25:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是涉谷正造的助导榷藤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.44,0:25:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场务的中岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.06,0:25:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正拍摄这还是第一次 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.17,0:25:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外行人一下子就做剧务是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.59,0:25:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是花了8年时间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.97,0:25:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,助手导演之路可是满是荆棘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为前辈先告诉你\N电影和色情片等级可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.28,0:25:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友好相处吧 呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.18,0:25:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.24,0:25:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 不说话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.07,0:25:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些人里面 我能行吗\N制作电影的基础也不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.06,0:25:55.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.74,0:26:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 你的话可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.35,0:26:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最开始全力以赴的话会接不上气的对吧 做做样子就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.67,0:26:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.52,0:26:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们见识下AV人的气势吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油 是男孩子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.86,0:26:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.41,0:26:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 “谁让你看到了眼泪”开机了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.10,0:26:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲的是身为老师的母亲\N和被孤立的女儿瞳之间爱和恨的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.30,0:26:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式拍一次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.24,0:26:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备 Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.92,0:26:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的小妹妹 和我们来玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.62,0:26:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边把内裤脱下来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.97,0:26:51.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然就只有这种程度呢 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.14,0:26:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 那种不温不火的演技
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.61,0:26:55.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.58,0:26:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少女的害羞的感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:27:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这么多人不可能镇静的脱掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.50,0:27:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是得装作镇静呐 好 再来一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.96,0:27:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CUT!不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.57,0:27:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CUT!CUT!CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.17,0:27:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息 到喝咖啡的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.07,0:27:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来我的房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.58,0:27:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.12,0:27:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.92,0:27:22.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 放松
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.92,0:27:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个当做是演技指导
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.40,0:27:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.86,0:27:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是美和小姐和翔子小姐\N第一次女孩子之间的亲密接触
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了很好的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.67,0:27:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱哦 翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.23,0:27:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要忘记这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.82,0:27:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK START!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.55,0:28:02.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.89,0:28:05.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 小看我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.80,0:28:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼在说谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.00,0:28:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CUT!CUT!CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:15.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊拉 看到没穿底裤了?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.02,0:28:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 就是这样 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.41,0:28:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,融入了感情 非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.94,0:28:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.36,0:28:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做到了 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.93,0:28:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天 瞳的母亲在学校\N被学生施以暴行的镜头开始
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.67,0:28:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 一起舒服一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.18,0:28:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.14,0:28:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下哟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.19,0:28:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.23,0:28:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.28,0:28:57.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的那个太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.15,0:28:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有演戏的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.19,0:29:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的 什么? 啊 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.06,0:29:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美那佳子小姐指名把我小金井纯平\N选作为高村澈的代演
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.05,0:29:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.00,0:29:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nice
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.60,0:29:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CUT!啊啦 额嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.53,0:30:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了 涉谷导演
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.59,0:30:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脑血栓 现在平静了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.59,0:30:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找一个代理导演 一定要把电影完成
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.61,0:30:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 加油到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.43,0:30:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.27,0:30:28.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 美和君
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.35,0:30:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能代替我当导演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.88,0:30:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.79,0:30:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 分镜制作是你的话\N应该是最理解我的想法的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.41,0:30:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.01,0:30:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.90,0:30:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演也好 成人影像也好 电影也好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.41,0:31:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,召集staff 指导演员的演技\N对于制作抱有热情比起这些
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.27,0:31:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是要有一颗对作品满含爱意的心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和有那样的心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.43,0:31:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和小姐 做吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.41,0:31:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.12,0:31:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和小姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.62,0:31:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉谷导演 我做做试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.52,0:31:28.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.68,0:31:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我们在 加油吧 美和
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.07,0:31:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.98,0:31:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们见识下成人影像的固执
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.05,0:31:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 把助导的我放在一边\N找什么成人小电影的导演代理
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.39,0:31:51.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榷藤先生 我们不合作的话\N电影可是拍不成的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.00,0:31:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 对呀 能行的话就做给我们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.66,0:31:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色情电影的导演能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.03,0:31:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.36,0:32:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?罢工?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.80,0:32:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摄影师 助导都在撂担子了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.27,0:32:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.16,0:32:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去求求他们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.51,0:32:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了 请协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.16,0:32:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不~行~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.83,0:32:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榷藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.22,0:32:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你过来了 若叶美和导演怎么不来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.58,0:32:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?那才是常识吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.02,0:32:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说拍电影了 连常识都不懂的家伙谁会跟随
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.14,0:32:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住 这个大外行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.18,0:32:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.73,0:32:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榷藤先生 请协助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.19,0:32:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.59,0:32:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...你们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.19,0:32:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也算是电影人吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.14,0:33:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.34,0:33:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小肚鸡肠的家伙们!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.82,0:33:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.30,0:33:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.65,0:33:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真敢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.20,0:33:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.38,0:33:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.02,0:33:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.82,0:33:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.17,0:33:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平 还不住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.32,0:33:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美和 不帮忙的家伙别管他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.53,0:33:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自己拍电影
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来当助导
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导演 快点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.68,0:33:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个场景 是作品的高潮
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.87,0:34:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳险些被退学的学生强暴
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.20,0:34:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在紧要关头赶来的母亲搭救
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.50,0:34:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 区区色情电影的导演 装的还挺像
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.85,0:34:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 本大爷一点都不受关注
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.05,0:34:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 给我等着 要把这部电影搞垮
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.25,0:34:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 只告诉你们一点儿有意思的事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.58,0:34:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.74,0:34:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 要和翔子做吗!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.31,0:34:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘 小声点
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.20,0:34:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式拍摄时让翔子吃我们的大屌 嘿嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.45,0:34:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.56,0:34:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备 开始!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.60,0:34:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住 住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.87,0:34:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.88,0:34:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.52,0:35:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.39,0:35:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.82,0:35:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.24,0:35:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了!一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.00,0:35:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.00,0:35:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.89,0:35:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别唧唧歪歪的!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.53,0:35:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.46,0:35:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.22,0:35:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呱!呱!怎么会!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.47,0:35:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个老太婆 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.92,0:36:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.44,0:36:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.51,0:36:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.62,0:36:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就是恐怖的电光毒龙钻
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.08,0:36:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.09,0:37:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦呵呵呵 为了亲爱的女儿\N妈妈连吸血鬼也能变哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.34,0:37:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.38,0:37:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.55,0:37:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.28,0:37:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CUT!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.78,0:37:22.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在美和小姐 还有阿波罗企划Stuff的大活跃下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.02,0:37:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电影成功杀青 在正月里 作为涉谷导演的代理 美和小姐导演过的事情也成为美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.42,0:37:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子小姐也在一夜之间\N成为家喻户晓的大明星
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.24,0:37:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的事情都成功解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.69,0:37:44.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜\N我们阿波罗企划这样也算是完成一部优秀影片了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.37,0:37:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏在这里的美那佳子小姐的精彩演出
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家 电影在正月里成为票房冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.30,0:37:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏这样三上翔子的人气也爆棚了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.51,0:37:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们终于对翔子的补偿也做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.63,0:38:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上翔子是我和涉谷的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.35,0:38:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离婚之后 翔子从小学开始就委托给保育园
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.33,0:38:11.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.71,0:38:14.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没发生太好了呢 纯平君
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我趁着这次机会也要隐退\N以后作为制片人在幕后工作
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.39,0:38:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.00,0:38:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐退吗 真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.50,0:38:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿波罗幕后的救世主是三上翔子酱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.66,0:38:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 我的王子是纯平君 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.39,0:38:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉凉的 好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.50,0:38:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的美和小姐的表情是认真地
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:38:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.02,0:38:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起来吧 美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.83,0:39:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么时候都会在美和小姐的身边的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.49,0:39:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么呀 身边怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.53,0:39:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.31,0:39:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 藏到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.12,0:39:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总而言之 第二次冒险也圆满结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.95,0:39:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.85,0:42:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预告
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.88,0:42:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好 我是纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.58,0:42:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的第二部作品 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.89,0:42:47.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 下回的《那些年冒过的险》
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.87,0:42:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到AV界的我和美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.10,0:42:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要帮助一个女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.13,0:42:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令人震惊的是她竟然是那个涉谷导演的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.62,0:43:00.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么 纯平
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.91,0:43:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我的秘书出演色情电影?不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.98,0:43:11.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原谅 绝对不可原谅 怎么会有这种好事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.06,0:43:12.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.98,0:43:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 好吧 给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进退两难的境地 涉谷导演又是高兴又是感慨
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.45,0:43:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 那位秘书在拍摄我们电影之前\N竟然被诱拐并且监禁起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.74,0:43:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得知那件事的纯平君去营救她
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.33,0:43:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却被狠狠的修理了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.10,0:43:51.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君真的是很没用
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.67,0:43:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么办法嘛 美和小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.06,0:43:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我就是弱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.69,0:44:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯平君 不要沮丧 我们可是有闭锁的橱柜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.00,0:44:16.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭锁的橱柜?
